01:58.814 --> 01:59.771
[car horn honks]

01:59.815 --> 02:01.077
[Michelle]
[excited] Baby girl!

02:02.252 --> 02:03.210
[car horn honks again]

02:03.253 --> 02:04.341
[Libby breathes deeply]

02:04.385 --> 02:06.691
[car engine rumbling]

02:11.957 --> 02:14.395
Soooo What do you think?

02:15.700 --> 02:17.137
I miss the Red.

02:17.180 --> 02:18.573
Boo. You're no fun.

02:19.965 --> 02:21.141
[softly] I know.

02:23.447 --> 02:24.927
Well, how was camp?

02:24.970 --> 02:26.972
Any good digs?

02:27.016 --> 02:28.713
Yeah. Some.

02:28.757 --> 02:29.758
And the other kids?

02:31.629 --> 02:33.196
Fine.

02:33.240 --> 02:34.589
[overly playful]
And the boooooys?

02:37.418 --> 02:39.115
Oh. That nice, huh?

02:39.159 --> 02:40.421
[smirks]

03:01.181 --> 03:02.182
Don't.

03:04.053 --> 03:06.055
♪ 'Cause we're
Girls girls girls girls ♪

03:06.098 --> 03:08.405
♪ And we like
Boys boys boys boys ♪

